Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:34.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:38.79,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Her family broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:41.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and Rukia is the only \Nrelative she has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.20,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,D-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.94,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Please let her stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:49.05,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,It’s so sad. It’s almost \Nlike in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.32,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.97,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I’d let her stay even if
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,her story wasn’t like the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.68,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ve seen this all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:02.51,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to ask me anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.61,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are…movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:06.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the part that bugs you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.81,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It’s as if I have \Nfour daughters now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:13.43,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like a harem, right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The words “daughters” and \N“harem” are not supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to go hand-in-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.99,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,We’re a loud family,\Nbut don’t let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:25.91,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.83,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.63,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Call us if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.11,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And put on your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.18,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:39.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.21,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,No. It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.43,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How many times is that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.10,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi, stay here and \Nwatch TV or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kon, change with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.61,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.14,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.65,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nozomi home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.17,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.80,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,She’s probably bored,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so do you mind keeping her company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.12,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what’s wrong with Kon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.05,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:40.15,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sir… We’ve lost all \Ncontact with the captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.79,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will rule the Soul Society \Nwith my invasion force. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.55,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until now, they were \Nholding back their power. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.51,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, this is {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.80,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the true power of Reigai! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.08,B2,UNOHANA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir, wait! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.48,B2,UNOHANA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we lose you, the Head Captain,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Thirteen Court Guard Squads \Nare bound to fall apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:15.88,B2,UNOHANA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must fall back and regroup \Nfor the time being. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.41,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.95,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,it’s very hard to believe that all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the captains will be \Ndefeated so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.49,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,And the transmission
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke Urahara received \Nmay not be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.99,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need to comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.63,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, right now, other than the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,lieutenants here in the World \Nof the Living, the only
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,battle-ready people are Ichigo \NKurosaki and his group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.74,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We need to prepare for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,an assault by the invasion \Nforce as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:53.98,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve noticed Hollows \Nappearing in large numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.81,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the power balance between the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,World of the Living and the \NSoul Society is disrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s inevitable that \Nmore Hollows would appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:05.95,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Our fears have now become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.51,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll deal with them with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the fighting forces we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:11.37,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Defending the World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from Hollows is certainly important,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.59,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,but be very careful not to give
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:18.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza’s invasion force an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:18.92,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.33,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.03,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.24,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What? You killed it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.78,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikkaku, you’re okay to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.87,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you’re talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:51.53,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how’s that \NMod Soul girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:57.11,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,She’s… Well, she \Ndid look a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.55,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The very first Mod Soul developed… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.89,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:23.55,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.30,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I supposed to say to her now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.32,B2,CAMPAIGN GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.35,B2,CAMPAIGN GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,We’re doing a promotion right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.78,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.70,B2,CAMPAIGN GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re doing a promotion right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.77,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s defective.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t even want one. This blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you’re not going to do it right,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don’t make them in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.53,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.09,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Since you weren’t here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve had to stay a Soul \NReaper all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and swap back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.27,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.81,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.86,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the spicy mayonnaise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.26,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Just mix it into the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.47,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not making any sense, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.44,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re asking me about Kujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.94,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t pretend like you \Ndidn’t know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.87,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.72,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I found it odd that I didn’t \Nsense any Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from her when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:58.21,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,When she healed Kurosaki’s injuries…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:02.02,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I became almost \Ncertain she was a Mod Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.76,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Her power was like Kido,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was a different sort of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.16,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,As a possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:15.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be an \Nartificially created ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.06,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a Mod Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:27.30,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one big \Nquestion that still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.79,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I have retrieved Nozomi, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:38.78,B2,KAGEROZA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will be able to show \Nyou my true power. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.33,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll need to know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:46.99,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.45,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it’s done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.84,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime’s special…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.72,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Choconomiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.89,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Choconomi…yaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:01.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Does this fall under the category \Nof chocolate, or okonomiyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.31,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I would say…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.23,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,It falls under yakisoba noodles \Nwith special sauce, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.77,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it’s none of the above?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.55,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.12,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.55,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.45,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, come back and make dinner too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.17,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.82,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.60,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be a father to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.09,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Dirty old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.50,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Choconomiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.08,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.09,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.36,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,She’s calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.77,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.20,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you worrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.35,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:48.37,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.28,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.67,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.60,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.36,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,The originals aren’t fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.60,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I expected wounds like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.80,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I will see to it that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.27,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,the world learns of your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.20,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,How depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.46,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.12,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you shouting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.19,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sis! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.04,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Punch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.13,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:41.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to punch me, not kick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.85,B2,VOICE ON MONITOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, everyone at our store{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}gets a free “I’m the man Lion!”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.68,B2,LION,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m the man! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.73,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.75,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.86,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.20,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,We’re done with buying groceries for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.45,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.95,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.28,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.23,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.96,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s keeping Rukia?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:24.72,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.31,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I owe you one, Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:36.27,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you’re doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:40.65,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a good thing I was \Npassing by just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Everything’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You know, Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you come over \Nfor dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.62,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What brought that up? \NYou’re creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.54,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Inoue’s making dinner for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.79,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about Kon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.18,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:02.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t say wrong, \Nbut he’s got no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.98,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:09.97,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,He just found out that Kujo \Nis a Mod Soul like himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.23,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s tough for him to go around \Nbehaving like he was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I figured the \Nlivelier it is, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.80,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,So you actually worry \Nabout such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How insensitive do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:28.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is delicious, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.19,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.71,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, you’re a culinary genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.60,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.80,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother sure looks…energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.29,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,More like weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.50,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,No energy, he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.64,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Four-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to eat Inoue’s \Ncooking is a privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.01,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I wouldn’t mind him \Nlosing more of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.76,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,for a sewing obsessed idiot like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.02,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t grow if you don’t eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially your boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.73,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Sorry! I didn’t mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.08,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right. He’s weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.70,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Late onset adolescence, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.25,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This deep-fried fish rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.80,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.61,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The way it tickles the taste \Nbuds is out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.41,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,And this sauce! It’s too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Question her? What’s this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.40,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza is pursuing \Nher so relentlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.22,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,What threat does she represent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.95,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,With the showdown with \NKageroza looming,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we thought we should question her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:33.72,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Neither we, nor you,\Nknow enough about that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.08,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we should avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,any more casualties arising \Nfrom our ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.82,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t just our own opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.10,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We’re speaking on behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the surviving Thirteen \NCourt Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.32,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:53.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:58.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,She’s got things she’s \Nsensitive about too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.34,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Now’s really not the time \Nfor noble talk, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.87,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it’s a fact that the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,invasion force wiped out \Nthe captains of the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:17.52,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be taking on that \Nenemy here in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.96,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the casualties might not end
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with just us, or with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.18,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:27.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.45,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, Project Spearhead was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,conceived to prevent \NSoul Reaper casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:39.77,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,But now, many Soul Reapers \Nhave been injured
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and have fallen in order to \Nprotect that Mod Soul kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.58,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You have to admit, it’s ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You may have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they’re \Nborn into this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they have a right to keep living too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.20,B2,KON (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that’s it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:24.25,B2,KON (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That bastard created Mod Souls? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.40,B2,KON (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No wonder you couldn’t trust me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.89,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that’s not true. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.26,B2,KON (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:37.47,B2,KON (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You thought of me as nothing but \None of Kageroza’s creations! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.93,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kageroza didn’t create you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.35,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The very first Mod Soul developed… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.69,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.60,B2,NOZOMI (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.00,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.78,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now, many Soul Reapers \Nhave been injured {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have fallen in order to \Nprotect that Mod Soul kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.47,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to admit, it’s ironic. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.69,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got attitude, \Nbut you’re useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.55,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.62,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:28.41,B2,NOZOMI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only…I weren’t alive…\Neveryone would be… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.84,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lots of good things will happen \Nif you keep on living!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.88,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.87,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.31,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now run as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.67,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.80,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to…protect…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.13,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.22,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,For everyone’s sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.33,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.52,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You… Is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.39,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:12.60,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said you \Ndidn’t have a Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.81,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:19.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing out at \Nsuch a late hour anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.46,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.98,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t start that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.85,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:30.11,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone tries to protect me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.54,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I don’t have the power \Nto do the same for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:37.54,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But when I thought of \Nwanting to protect you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.13,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I had a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:51.52,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.47,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What was I so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.44,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I got all caught up on \Nwhat to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.19,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We may have been born as Mod Souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't let that \Nstop us from trying to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:04.68,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.41,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.26,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.91,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.45,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.49,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! It’s yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.37,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.46,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But it’s defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.84,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The mane came off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.93,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I like it better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.21,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.73,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.25,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ishida. How’d the dinner go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.27,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It went fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after Inoue finished cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I secretly went and \Nadjusted the flavoring,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so it all tasted good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \NI haven’t eaten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:30.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.30,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of feeding \Nsomeone who escaped into his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.79,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:40.77,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it’s almost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:42.81,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:46.45,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show off my cooking skills
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the power of Ryujinjakka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:52.49,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about dinner… Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.66,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.16,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I have that too. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:23:59.88,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.83,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,You’re well prepared, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:04.61,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,